Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.859 --> 00:00:08.300
 Let's make chops with cheese 

00:00:08.300 --> 00:00:34.720
 Cut pork loin into slices 1 cm thick. 

00:00:34.720 --> 00:01:02.860
 Beat off on both sides. 

00:01:02.860 --> 00:01:17.450
 Salt, pepper to taste, on both sides. 

00:01:17.450 --> 00:02:04.140
 Hard cheese cut into pieces. 

00:02:04.140 --> 00:02:35.980
 In each chop put two or three slices of cheese. 

00:02:35.980 --> 00:02:37.510
 Chop roll in half. 

00:02:37.510 --> 00:02:38.510
 Chop the edges of the chop and pin down with toothpicks 

00:02:38.510 --> 00:02:39.510
 from three sides. 

00:02:39.510 --> 00:03:45.760
 Beat eggs, I beat with a fork. 

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:49.239
 Prepare the flour. 

00:03:49.239 --> 00:03:59.409
 Every prepared chop roll well 

00:03:59.409 --> 00:04:00.409
 in flour. 

00:04:00.409 --> 00:04:05.129
 Then in a beaten egg. 

00:04:05.129 --> 00:04:26.720
 Put chops on a frying pan heated with vegetable oil, 

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:36.580
 fry, uncovered, until golden brown (by 

00:04:36.580 --> 00:04:59.840
 2-3 minutes on each side). 

00:04:59.840 --> 00:05:28.759
 The fire is closer to strong. 

00:05:28.759 --> 00:05:39.999
 Then transfer to a deep pan, put in 

00:05:39.999 --> 00:05:47.789
 preheated to 200C oven without covering 30 minutes. 

00:05:47.789 --> 00:05:53.869
 Serve with sauce. 

00:05:53.869 --> 00:05:56.289
 Enjoy your meal! 

